title: Keep Your Walls Up
itunes:title: Keep Your Walls Up
description:
While we can’t stop negative things from happening, the key is to have walls built up so we don’t allow everything to come in. You’ll learn if it’s not a positive, hopeful, productive, faith-filled thing, then don’t dwell on it.----Visit https://joelosteen.com to receive daily updates and encouragement from Joel Osteen.----Have you followed Joel Osteen on Instagram? https://instagram.com/joelosteen.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
